<h2 id="4-wrap-with-div">4. WRAP WITH DIV</h2>

<p>Wrap different sections in different <code class="highlighter-rouge">div</code> and name your <code class="highlighter-rouge">tag</code></p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"features"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
